query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!: i64"
            FROM coupons
            WHERE status = 'active'
                AND ($1::text IS NULL OR type::text = $1)
                AND ($2::text IS NULL OR (code ILIKE $2 OR name ILIKE $2))
                AND (valid_from IS NULL OR valid_from <= NOW())
                AND (valid_until IS NULL OR valid_until > NOW())
